OL,3,CHeadteacher jailed after attacking his
OL,4,Cdeputy due to "sexual jealousy"
OL,6,FA headteacher has been sentenced to
OL,7,Ftwo years and four months in jail
OL,8,Fafter attacking his deputy at their
OL,9,Fschool.
OL,11,FAnthony John Felton, 54, appeared at
OL,12,FSwansea Crown Court this morning after
OL,13,Fpleading guilty to grievous bodily
OL,14,Fharm with intent.
OL,16,FHe was in work at St John's Catholic
OL,17,FSchool and Sixth Form Centre when he
OL,18,Farmed himself with a wrench and
OL,19,Fattacked 51 year old Richard Pyke, on
OL,20,F5th March 2025.
