OL,3,CHeadteacher jailed after attacking his
OL,4,Cdeputy due to "sexual jealousy"
OL,6,FIeuan Rees, for the prosecution, said
OL,7,FFelton believed Mr Pyke had slept with
OL,8,Fanother teacher with whom he had
OL,9,Frecently been in a relationship.
OL,11,F"The evidence of his wife and the
OL,12,Fadmissions he made to her suggested Mr
OL,13,FFelton had been in a relationship with
OL,14,Fanother member of staff and had
OL,15,Frecently discovered he was the father
OL,16,Fof her child," he said.
OL,18,F"Furthermore, he believed that Mr Pyke
OL,19,Fhad now begun his own relationship
OL,20,Fwith that lady."
