OL,3,CHeadteacher jailed after attacking his
OL,4,Cdeputy due to "sexual jealousy"
OL,6,FFollowing the incident on March 5 this
OL,7,Fyear, Felton threw the wrench away and
OL,8,Fleft the school in his car.
OL,10,FHe then sent an email to all staff
OL,11,Fapologising "for the problems and
OL,12,Fdistress his actions were likely to
OL,13,Fcause".
OL,15,FAccording to an annual report, he was
OL,16,Fappointed at headteacher in September
OL,17,F2023.
OL,19,FJudge Paul Thomas KC sentenced him at
OL,20,FSwansea Crown Court on Friday to two
OL,21,Fyears and four months in jail.
