OL,3,CHeadteacher jailed after attacking his
OL,4,Cdeputy due to "sexual jealousy"
OL,6,FHe was also given a restraining order.
OL,8,FMr Thomas said an attack by a head on
OL,9,Ftheir deputy was "I suspect, entirely
OL,10,Fwithout precedent" and was the result
OL,11,Fof "overwhelming sexual jealousy".
OL,13,FFollowing the incident, police said Mr
OL,14,FPyke had been discharged from hospital
OL,15,Fafter suffering minor injuries.
