OL,3,CHeadteacher jailed after attacking his
OL,4,Cdeputy due to "sexual jealousy"
OL,6,FAbul Hussain of the Crown Prosecution
OL,7,FService said: "Anthony Felton struck a
OL,8,Fdefenceless man repeatedly to the head
OL,9,Fwith a metal weapon, demonstrating he
OL,10,Fhad an intent to cause his victim
OL,11,Freally serious harm.
OL,13,F"The level of unprovoked violence,
OL,14,Ffrom a professional in the workplace,
OL,15,Fwas shocking.
OL,17,F"Too often we see attacks of this
OL,18,Fnature result in life changing
OL,19,Finjuries or fatal consequences, and
OL,20,Fthankfully, that was not the result in
OL,21,Fthis case."
