OL,4,Cdeputy due to "sexual jealousy"
OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Simon Davies of
OL,7,FSouth Wales Police said
OL,9,F"Anthony Felton's actions have
OL,10,Fresulted in him going to prison, have
OL,11,Fhad a significant impact on his
OL,12,Fpersonal life and have destroyed his
OL,13,Fdecades-long teaching career ` not to
OL,14,Fmention the physical impact upon the
OL,15,Fvictim, who we are pleased is on the
OL,16,Froad to recovery.
